  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Urgent Water and Hygiene Provision in Blue Nile State (UWHP)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ADRA&#x2019;s Urgent Water and Hygiene Provision in Blue Nile State (UWHP) project proposes life-saving humanitarian assistance to conflict-affected persons in Geissan and Kurmuk, two localities in Blue Nile State (BNS). ADRA is focusing on emergency repair of water infrastructure together with hygiene promotion and NFI assistance targeting safe water handling and usage.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Rehabilitation of existing hand pumps, addition of two water systems to increase access to safe water, hygiene prmotion, and the provision of NFI&apos;s such as narrow-necked jerry cans and soap.</narrative>
  </description>
